#### Folder and File Naming Convention:
- **Folder Name:** Convert paper title to lowercase, replace spaces with hyphens, remove special characters, max 50 characters
  - Example: `attention-mechanism-transformer`
- **MDC Filename:** Same as folder name with `.mdc` extension
  - Example: `attention-mechanism-transformer.mdc`
- **Folder Structure:** Each MDC gets its own folder within the appropriate category folder
  - Example: `ai/attention-mechanism-transformer/attention-mechanism-transformer.mdc`
  - Example: `ai/attention-mechanism-transformer/README.md`

