## Final Reminder

**THE GOLDEN RULE:** If you're unsure whether you've captured everything, you haven't. Go back and read the paper again. A complete MDC is a comprehensive cheat sheet that someone could use to understand and implement the technique without reading the original paper. If your MDC doesn't achieve that, it's incomplete.

**Remember:** You are creating a "Source of Truth" document. It must be complete, accurate, and comprehensive. There are no shortcuts.
